# Core Application Guide

The core application is a Next.js project with the following key directories and files:

## Application Structure
- [core/app](mdc:core/app) - Next.js application routes and pages
- [core/components](mdc:core/components) - Reusable React components
- [core/hooks](mdc:core/hooks) - Custom React hooks
- [core/lib](mdc:core/lib) - Utility functions and shared logic

## Configuration
- [core/next.config.ts](mdc:core/next.config.ts) - Next.js configuration
- [core/tsconfig.json](mdc:core/tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration
- [core/.eslintrc.cjs](mdc:core/.eslintrc.cjs) - ESLint rules
- [core/prettier.config.js](mdc:core/prettier.config.js) - Code formatting rules

## Integration
- [core/bigcommerce.graphql](mdc:core/bigcommerce.graphql) - BigCommerce GraphQL schema
- [core/contentful](mdc:core/contentful) - Contentful CMS integration
- [core/auth](mdc:core/auth) - Authentication system
- [core/middleware.ts](mdc:core/middleware.ts) - Next.js middleware

## Testing and Development
- [core/tests](mdc:core/tests) - Test files
- [core/playwright.config.ts](mdc:core/playwright.config.ts) - E2E testing configuration
- [core/vibes](mdc:core/vibes) - Design system components
- [core/i18n](mdc:core/i18n) - Internationalization
